Main Idea

- scrapes news of fincancial website like yahoo in real time
- analyzes the news sentiment using NLP (if its postive news or negative news) or neutral
- Stores and vizualies data alongside the stock prices
- sends the alerts to the email or summarizes the sentsentiment shifts
- overall helps the user invest into a stock

- We will only be looking at apple stock and then get into more later on

VADER

- it gives the new tilte a score based of the words in it
  for example ["Apple stock surges after strong earnings!"]
  - surges (good word)
  - strong (good word)
  - after (neutral doesnt effect the score)

